CloneBackend.name: CloneBackend
CloneBackend.description:
Grants permission to clone an existing Amplify Admin backend environment into a new

CreateBackend.name: CreateBackend
CreateBackend.description: Grants permission to create a new Amplify Admin backend environment by Amplify appId
